data.description: This Stunning remodeled POOL home on the mesa leaves nothing to be desired. Over 2400 sqft, this 4 bedroom home includes two master suites with on suite baths. The upgraded kitchen features solid surface Living Stone Counters, 5 burner 36 inch cooktop, Jenn-Air double ovens, pantry and a breakfast bar. The family room opens to the kitchen and has a wood burning stove with brick surround. The main master bedroom is huge and has a wet bar as well as access to a large bathroom which includes dual sinks with solid surface counters that match the kitchen as well as a remodeled shower with tile surrround. The interior beauty of this home can only be outdone by its exterior. Outside there is a giant kidney shaped pool with spa, 2 patios for entertaining, lush mature landscaping with auto sprinklers and a block wall which surrounds the entire property. Other amenities include indoor laundry, formal and everyday dining rooms, enclosed patio cabana, front circle drive, RV parking and more.
